es end well? It's up to you. Ration food and water, make best use of your supplies, face difficult choices and even venture into the wasteland.\n\nGood luck.\n\nEXPERIENCE\nthe suburbian nightmare of a nuke dropping down on your neighbourhood in this atomic, dark comedy set in 1950s.\n\nSCAVENGE\nany supplies, you will need to survive, and family members in a 60 second rush through your randomly generated house.\n\nPREPARE\nfor the worst. Don’t just grab arbitrary items, plan your survival and follow helpful tips from emergency broadcasts!\n\nSURVIVE\nin a fallout shelter with whatever you brought with you. How many days will you last? Will everyone make it out alive?\n\nDECIDE\nwhat to do, when the post-apocalyptic world pushes you to the corner. Will you risk going outside? Who is not eating dinner, when barely any food is left? How do you deal with a mutant cockroach infestation?","rating":80.0,"popularity":1.0,"total_rating":80.0,"total_rating_count":0,"rating_count":0,"games":[43130,28277,41895,74378,25311,26145,44242,22425,28465,37419],"tags":[268435469,268435487],"category":0,"genres":[13,31],"first_release_date":1474502400000,"platforms":[39],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":39,"date":1474502400000,"region":8,"human":"2016-Sep-22","y":2016,"m":9}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/usvymokxssdnyzzbclie.jpg","cloudinary_id":"usvymokxssdnyzzbclie","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/jrgp0vxuebsc19mxgtj8.jpg","cloudinary_id":"jrgp0vxuebsc19mxgtj8","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/iybfualto6tcmyqxjiqd.jpg","cloudinary_id":"iybfualto6tcmyqxjiqd","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/gjyjfk7y2w4drwecfefn.jpg","cloudinary_id":"gjyjfk7y2w4drwecfefn","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/zod0itx6yahremdak6pg.jpg","cloudinary_id":"zod0itx6yahremdak6pg","width":552