cles with letters in the right sequence.\nThe coloring mode will be especially appreciated by young artists. In this mode, you can proceed to coloring pictures without connecting points. To make the process even more exciting, you can change any predefined color. To do this, press and hold the paint bucket and choose the necessary color from the palette.","rating":90.0,"popularity":1.0,"total_rating":90.0,"total_rating_count":0,"rating_count":0,"category":0,"themes":[35],"first_release_date":1418774400000,"platforms":[14],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":14,"date":1418774400000,"region":8,"human":"2014-Dec-17","y":2014,"m":12}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/wcuhlej6kzcx9ac7nj7g.jpg","cloudinary_id":"wcuhlej6kzcx9ac7nj7g","width":800,"height":500},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/avbo1s2wps6ysprxzfnp.jpg","cloudinary_id":"avbo1s2wps6ysprxzfnp","width":800,"height":500},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/gsrnlfca7am2zcyabn3k.jpg","cloudinary_id":"gsrnlfca7am2zcyabn3k","width":800,"height":500},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/mxorkpnvhqmzmlu4lbrz.jpg","cloudinary_id":"mxorkpnvhqmzmlu4lbrz","width":800,"height":500},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/oiyvdzpjyhxernltxeyb.jpg","cloudinary_id":"oiyvdzpjyhxernltxeyb","width":800,"height":500}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/bcdogqfpcgzx0ppzm0y6.jpg","cloudinary_id":"bcdogqfpcgzx0ppzm0y6","width":512,"height":512}},{"id":86726,"name":"Word Puzzle Game","slug":"word-puzzle-game","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/word-puzzle-game","created_at":1518601682223,"updated_at":1518705556783,"summary":"Join thousands of players who exercise their brains every day with the best crossword game now available for Mac. Word Puzzle Game is a fun and engaging game.\n\nA Word Puzzle Game is a word puzzle that normally takes the form of a square or a rectangular grid of white and black shaded squa