, Christmas \u0026 Winter, Clothes, Countries, Elements, Foods, Fruits \u0026 Veggies, Human Body, Kings \u0026 Pirates, Plants \u0026 Trees, Sports and French Random. \n\nExpand your vocabulary! In app dictionary lookups from 1 of 6 reference sites allows you to learn more about words you did not know. This is really great for those SAT word lists. \n\nFeatures: \n* 4 different themes to choose from. \n* 73 word categories including 7 random modes with advanced engine to avoid repeats. \n* Both 1 player and 2 player modes. \n* In 2 player mode one player enters a word for the other to guess. \n* Play as long as you can, after each correct word a new scene and word appears. \n* Helps increase both vocabulary and spelling ability. \n* Great background music and sound effects. \n* Fun and educational at the same. \n* Auto-save when you close it (cmd + Q) so you can continue where you left off (1 player). \n\nWe hope you enjoy Ultimate Hangman!","popularity":1.0,"category":0,"keywords":[1361,2366],"first_release_date":1296950400000,"platforms":[14],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":14,"date":1296950400000,"region":8,"human":"2011-Feb-06","y":2011,"m":2}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/yznmauk5xic9uopowlpk.jpg","cloudinary_id":"yznmauk5xic9uopowlpk","width":800,"height":500},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/la3gqi3akgphuvgwmuus.jpg","cloudinary_id":"la3gqi3akgphuvgwmuus","width":800,"height":500},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/cndxkvonrszdrvr6gxdu.jpg","cloudinary_id":"cndxkvonrszdrvr6gxdu","width":800,"height":500},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/xvjfxywe5lp0zfnfwqck.jpg","cloudinary_id":"xvjfxywe5lp0zfnfwqck","width":800,"height":500},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/yejnx1scgy7yjtoj8io1.jpg","cloudinary_id":"yejnx1scgy7yjtoj8io1","width":800,"height":500}],"cover":{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/eg2hef5agw7yjcf8cv4d.jpg","clou