etup Game” module.\n• CENTRE function to align the board to the centre.\n• Option to show the LEGAL MOVES for current piece (very useful for novice players)\n• Option to ROTATE the board in ‘two player’ mode.\n• Help button with instructions for En Passant capture / Castling (activated automatically).\n• Option to limit ‘think time’ in ‘one player’ mode to 5, 15 or 30 seconds\n• Option to switch on / off sound effects and / or music\n• Automatically saves the current state of the game, so the game state would be automatically restored if you quit the application\n• Universal app (supports iPad / iPod touch / iPhone)\n\nIf you love playing chess in portrait mode and in 2D, then download and try out our Chess Prime app (100,000+ downloads so far)!\n\nEnjoy!","rating":90.0,"popularity":1.0,"total_rating":90.0,"total_rating_count":0,"rating_count":0,"games":[11362,9760,33603,36962,55888,73075,65827,2015,32283,75065],"tags":[268435471,536872273],"category":0,"keywords":[1361],"genres":[15],"first_release_date":1434412800000,"platforms":[39],"release_dates":[{"category":0,"platform":39,"date":1434412800000,"region":8,"human":"2015-Jun-16","y":2015,"m":6}],"screenshots":[{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/ev3ofaffndwzzmztlq8m.jpg","cloudinary_id":"ev3ofaffndwzzmztlq8m","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/yobbzqaralcytiii1wun.jpg","cloudinary_id":"yobbzqaralcytiii1wun","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/l8qutrs19vuzuzpblofm.jpg","cloudinary_id":"l8qutrs19vuzuzpblofm","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/hm1jsdv13m3rqdwkr26r.jpg","cloudinary_id":"hm1jsdv13m3rqdwkr26r","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/cwgkred21osmev7xwxzd.jpg","cloudinary_id":"cwgkred21osmev7xwxzd","width":552,"height":414},{"url":"//images.igdb.com/igdb/image/upload/t_thumb/nzlgdgiayd5numyqu8xf.jpg","cloudinary_id":"nzlgdgi